<para id="fs-id1169596685318">To find a third solution, we’ll let <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> and solve for <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math>.</para>
