</media>
<para id="fs-id1169594160564">The ordered pair <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> is a solution to <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. We will add it to <link target-id="fs-id1169596386254"/>.</para>
